                    </div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold">Collaboration Portal</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted">Interactive discussions and knowledge sharing among students and teachers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="ll-card h-100 p-4 text-center">
                    <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: #cffafe; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem;">
