            <p class="lead text-muted">Comprehensive knowledge management for educational institutions</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="ll-card p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <div style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
                            <i class="bi bi-archive fs-4 text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="fw-bold">1. Knowledge Repository Module</h5>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-0">Upload, organize, and manage all educational resources including PDFs, reviewers, study guides, and learning materials with easy search and retrieval.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="ll-card p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <div style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
                            <i class="bi bi-shield-lock fs-4 text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="fw-bold">2. Policy & Procedure Module</h5>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-0">Set access policies, manage file versions, control access duration, and track change history for all educational materials.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="ll-card p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <div style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
                            <i class="bi bi-journal-text fs-4 text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="fw-bold">3. Lesson Learned Module</h5>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-0">Allow users to input ratings, comments, insights, and learnings. Track reading history so users can continue where they left off.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="ll-card p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <div style="width: 56px; height: 56px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #7c3aed); border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;">
